FBIS3-49342 "dreeu006_d_94010" FBIS-EEU-94-006 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Jan 1994 SLOVAKIA Ethnic Hungarians Kept From Attending Meeting LD0801150294 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network in Hungarian 1400 GMT 8 Jan 94 LD0801150294 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network Language: Hungarian Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] In Slovakia, police prevented representatives from Districts Lucenec and Filakovo from getting to the meeting of Zitny Ostrov localities. [passage omitted] First policemen asked for documents certifying the payment of road tax, which is levied on weekends. After these documents were presented, they took away vehicle registration documents without giving any reason. They only told the protesting passengers that whatever they did, the buses could not leave the territory of the Slovak district.
